Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:10.83,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:16.01,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.....Rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:23.15,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今日が過去に変わる事で、明日が近づいて。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:30.40,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな当たり前の事に　心は傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:34.48,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}あの日見た『世界』を　もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:39.97,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}叶う時が　いつか来るなら　もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:47.76,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まるで可能性が無いと　誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:52.62,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}次の君に逢える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:56.57,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繰り返し　巡る運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:59.93,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}たとえ　どんな道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:03.56,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}決して　決して　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:07.33,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『あした、またね。』　その『未来』を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:11.12,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつまでも失くさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.67,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}終わりのない始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:20.05,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今、君と夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:24.80,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繋いだ手を　離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.98,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:31.65,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:33.86,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change.
