Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳  佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  你  你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的不是的  什麼都沒做  我什麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個人倒在這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  不過還是有呼吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  是不是叫輛救護車比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  還是說應該先叫老師來呢  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認識她？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不認識啦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  你認識我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認識我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是  結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是  古川結
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川同學
